This work builds on / uses:
- GF180MCU Open PDK (GlobalFoundries / Google / efabless), Apache-2.0 — used as
  the target technology; not redistributed here.
- LibreCell (lclayout, Z3 SMT), AGPL-3.0 — used as a TOOL to generate cell
  layouts. The generated cells are this project's own work, not a derivative of
  the tool. The community GF180MCU lclayout enablement (LibreSilicon) was adapted
  under librecell/tech_gf180mcu/ with documented patches.

Cell architecture follows:
- Belluomini et al., "Limited switch dynamic logic circuits for high-speed
  low-power circuit design," IBM J. Res. & Dev. 50(2/3), 2006.
- Sivagnaname et al., "Wide Limited Switch Dynamic Logic Circuit
  Implementations," 2006.
(These papers are NOT redistributed in this repository.)
